summary: a small mod i created that adds a large and powerful mudcrab to the game.
descriptionHtml:
a simple mod i created and experimented with. i decided to release this anyways. it seems to replace all mudcrabs with this one once you reach level 35 though so I\'ll try to fix that. 

oh yeah and this guy has 3k hp. 

my now full time project is a complete set of fairly difficult high level enemies for those of us level 35+.
author: keiskay
